<title>USA: MBf USA completes private placement.</title>
<headline>MBf USA completes private placement.</headline>
<dateline>ITASCA, Ill. 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>MBf USA Inc said Wednesday it sold 672,269 shares of its common stock in a private placement to its majority shareholder, MBf International Ltd, for $1 million, a 15 percent discount from the August 20 closing price.</p>
<p>Proceeds will be used as working capital, the company said. Based on the increased number of shares outstanding, MBf International's ownership in MBf USA increased to 68 percent, the company said.</p>
<p>--Reuters Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787</p>
